  <summary date="2015-07-13T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Urges: (1) the Federation Internationale de Football Association to eliminate gender pay inequity and treat all athletes with respect and dignity; and (2) all other local, state, federal, and international organizations to eliminate gender pay inequity.

